  <entry>
    <title>如何在 dva 中使用 sass</title>
    <link href="http://blog.formulangel.com/2016/10/26/integrate-sass-with-dva/"/>
    <id>http://blog.formulangel.com/2016/10/26/integrate-sass-with-dva/</id>
    <published>2016-10-26T09:47:01.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-02-17T09:27:47.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>安装 sass-loader 和 node-sass 之后，在 webpack.config.js 中</p>
<figure class="highlight fortran"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">webpackConfig.<span class="keyword">module</span>.loaders.forEach(<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span><span class="params">(loader, index)</span></span> &#123;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>之上（其实只要在这个 function 里面都可以），添加以下代码：</p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="selector-tag">webpackConfig</span><span class="selector-class">.module</span><span class="selector-class">.loaders</span><span class="selector-class">.push</span>(&#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">test</span>: /\.module\.sass$/,</div><div class="line">  loader: path.<span class="built_in">join</span>(path.dirname(require.resolve(<span class="string">'extract-text-webpack-plugin'</span>)), <span class="string">'loader.js'</span>) + <span class="string">'?&#123;"remove":true&#125;!css?sourceMap&amp;modules&amp;localIdentName=[local]___[hash:base64:5]&amp;-autoprefixer!'</span> + <span class="string">'postcss-loader!'</span>+ <span class="string">'sass-loader?sourceMap'</span></div><div class="line">&#125;);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<a id="more"></a>
<p>然后在 </p>
<figure class="highlight fortran"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">webpackConfig.<span class="keyword">module</span>.loaders.forEach(<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span><span class="params">(loader, index)</span></span> &#123;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>之下添加以下代码即可：</p>
<figure class="highlight gradle"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (typeof loader.test === <span class="string">'function'</span> &amp;&amp; loader.test.toString().indexOf(<span class="string">'\\.sass$'</span>) &gt; -<span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">  loader.<span class="keyword">include</span> = <span class="regexp">/node_modules/</span>;</div><div class="line">  loader.test = <span class="regexp">/\.sass$/</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (loader.test.toString() === <span class="string">'/\\.module\\.sass$/'</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">  loader.<span class="keyword">exclude</span> = <span class="regexp">/node_modules/</span>;</div><div class="line">  loader.test = <span class="regexp">/\.sass$/</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;安装 sass-loader 和 node-sass 之后，在 webpack.config.js 中&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight fortran&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;webpackConfig.&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;module&lt;/span&gt;.loaders.forEach(&lt;span class=&quot;function&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;params&quot;&gt;(loader, index)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;#123;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;p&gt;之上（其实只要在这个 function 里面都可以），添加以下代码：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight css&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;selector-tag&quot;&gt;webpackConfig&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;selector-class&quot;&gt;.module&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;selector-class&quot;&gt;.loaders&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;selector-class&quot;&gt;.push&lt;/span&gt;(&amp;#123;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;attribute&quot;&gt;test&lt;/span&gt;: /\.module\.sass$/,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;  loader: path.&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;join&lt;/span&gt;(path.dirname(require.resolve(&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;extract-text-webpack-plugin&#39;&lt;/span&gt;)), &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;loader.js&#39;&lt;/span&gt;) + &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;?&amp;#123;&quot;remove&quot;:true&amp;#125;!css?sourceMap&amp;amp;modules&amp;amp;localIdentName=[local]___[hash:base64:5]&amp;amp;-autoprefixer!&#39;&lt;/span&gt; + &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;postcss-loader!&#39;&lt;/span&gt;+ &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;sass-loader?sourceMap&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&amp;#125;);&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>如何在 angular2-webpack-starter 中使用 font-awesome</title>
    <link href="http://blog.formulangel.com/2016/06/23/integrate-font-awesome-with-angular2-webpack-starter/"/>
    <id>http://blog.formulangel.com/2016/06/23/integrate-font-awesome-with-angular2-webpack-starter/</id>
    <published>2016-06-23T07:23:13.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-02-17T09:27:47.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>如果你跟我一样是用 <a href="https://github.com/AngularClass/angular2-webpack-starter" target="_blank" rel="external">angular2-webpack-starter</a> 作为 Angular2 的脚手架的话，就可能在整合 font-awesome 时遇到问题。</p>
<p>因为此脚手架的设定是用 <code>raw-loader</code> 来载入 CSS：</p>
<figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">/*</div><div class="line"> * Raw loader support <span class="keyword">for</span> *.css <span class="keyword">files</span></div><div class="line"> * Returns <span class="keyword">file</span> content <span class="keyword">as</span> <span class="built_in">string</span></div><div class="line"> *</div><div class="line"> * See: http<span class="variable">s:</span>//github.<span class="keyword">com</span>/webpack/raw-loader</div><div class="line"> */</div><div class="line">&#123;</div><div class="line">  tes<span class="variable">t:</span> /\.css$/,</div><div class="line">  loader: <span class="string">'raw-loader'</span></div><div class="line">&#125;,</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>而 font-awesome 因为资源文件需要导入的原因就要用到 <code>css-loader</code> 和 <code>style-loader</code>，用 <code>raw-loader</code> 就载入不了图标了。<br><a id="more"></a></p>
<h3 id="解决方案"><a href="#解决方案" class="headerlink" title="解决方案"></a>解决方案</h3><p>首先安装 <code>css-loader</code> 和 <code>style-loader</code>:</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">cnpm <span class="keyword">install</span> -D css-loader <span class="keyword">style</span>-loader</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>因为 <code>raw-loader</code> 的匹配正则被设置为 <code>\.css$</code>, 所以我们可以把 <code>?</code> 问号加在行尾来 bypass 此正则，即使用以下代码来载入 <code>font-awesome</code>：</p>
<figure class="highlight maxima"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">require('<span class="built_in">style</span>-loader!css-loader!<span class="built_in">font</span>-awesome/css/<span class="built_in">font</span>-awesome.css?');</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然后图标就可以正常显示了：</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;i <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">"fa fa-floppy-o"</span> aria-hidden=<span class="string">"true"</span>&gt;<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span></span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;如果你跟我一样是用 &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/AngularClass/angular2-webpack-starter&quot;&gt;angular2-webpack-starter&lt;/a&gt; 作为 Angular2 的脚手架的话，就可能在整合 font-awesome 时遇到问题。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;因为此脚手架的设定是用 &lt;code&gt;raw-loader&lt;/code&gt; 来载入 CSS：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight vim&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;5&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;6&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;7&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;8&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;9&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;10&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;/*&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt; * Raw loader support &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; *.css &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;files&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt; * Returns &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;file&lt;/span&gt; content &lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt; *&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt; * See: http&lt;span class=&quot;variable&quot;&gt;s:&lt;/span&gt;//github.&lt;span class=&quot;keyword&quot;&gt;com&lt;/span&gt;/webpack/raw-loader&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt; */&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&amp;#123;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;  tes&lt;span class=&quot;variable&quot;&gt;t:&lt;/span&gt; /\.css$/,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;  loader: &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&#39;raw-loader&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&amp;#125;,&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;p&gt;而 font-awesome 因为资源文件需要导入的原因就要用到 &lt;code&gt;css-loader&lt;/code&gt; 和 &lt;code&gt;style-loader&lt;/code&gt;，用 &lt;code&gt;raw-loader&lt;/code&gt; 就载入不了图标了。&lt;br&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
